@MetricsApi_HostAddress = https://localhost:5001
@AccessToken = eyJ...replace-with-real-token...

### Submit a test result (requires bearer token)
POST {{MetricsApi_HostAddress}}/api/tests/result
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"buildId": "build-123",
	"testName": "Example.Test",
	"outcome": "Passed",
	"durationSeconds": 12.34,
	"completedAt": "2025-10-04T12:00:00Z"
}

### Get test summary
GET {{MetricsApi_HostAddress}}/api/tests/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Clear results
POST {{MetricsApi_HostAddress}}/api/tests/clear
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
